Package us.ihmc.euclid.geometry.interfaces

Interface Vertex2DSupplier

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConvexPolygon2DBasics, ConvexPolygon2DReadOnly, FixedFrameConvexPolygon2DBasics, FrameConvexPolygon2DBasics, FrameConvexPolygon2DReadOnly, FrameVertex2DSupplier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConvexPolygon2D, FrameConvexPolygon2D
    public interface Vertex2DSupplier
    Implement this interface to create a custom supplier of 2D vertices or use the static methods to create default suppliers.
    Author:
    Sylvain Bertrand
